omes a target after one of his theories turns out to be true. Unfortunately, in order to save himself, he has to figure out which theory it is.","genre_ids":[28,18,9648,53],"popularity":2.2702,"vote_count":1589,"poster_path":"/sTyTKZVikQU6g50HE8HR1tBSRxj.jpg","release_date":"1997-08-08","vote_average":6.617,"backdrop_path":"/70tmPOoCJCciWaM1vDvXAi4w3Bc.jpg","original_title":"Conspiracy Theory","original_language":"en"},{"id":9292,"adult":false,"title":"Hudson Hawk","video":false,"overview":"Eddie Hawkins, called Hudson Hawk has just been released from ten years of prison and is planning to spend the rest of his life honestly. But then the crazy Mayflower couple blackmail him to steal some of the works of Leonardo da Vinci. If he refuses, they threaten to kill his friend Tommy.","genre_ids":[28,12,35],"popularity":2.7553,"vote_count":1108,"poster_path":"/2AiR7HZuIOUdJp6LYOEOA8z7pF3.jpg","release_date":"1991-05-23","vote_average":5.705,"backdrop_path":"/h0zbeNCOd2eKpFGmJGPLOrp5wP4.jpg","original_title":"Hudson Hawk","original_language":"en"},{"id":9311,"adult":false,"title":"Smilla's Sense of Snow","video":false,"overview":"Smilla Jaspersen attempts to understand the death of a small boy who falls from the roof of her apartment building. Suspecting wrongdoing, Smilla uncovers a trail of clues leading towards a secretive corporation that has made several mysterious expeditions to Greenland.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":0.8232,"vote_count":254,"poster_path":"/2BwL0fKCaNRXfqMsu2uvFFS7dZX.jpg","release_date":"1997-02-28","vote_average":6.293,"backdrop_path":"/4TQgxCYdaizZr9bfjQYVsZPZVGE.jpg","original_title":"Smilla's Sense of Snow","original_language":"en"},{"id":9313,"adult":false,"title":"The Man in the Iron Mask","video":false,"overview":"Years have passed since the Three Musketeers, Aramis, Athos and Porthos, have fought together with their friend, D'Artagnan. But with the tyrannical King Louis using his power to wreak havoc in the kingdom while his twin brother